  "body": "<p>Hello everyone! I am Violeta Scrap and I am delightful to come back to Amy Tangerine’s blog to show you one of the first Layouts that I have made with her new collection “Hustle &amp; Heart” combined with elements from the collection “On a Whim”.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bc18c7e26c52ab21.jpg?v=1782539877\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>To create this Layout, I have used as a base for the project a paper with a simple design. I have added some transparent stickers around the pictures to create the composition. I have used different transparent stickers from the collection “On a Whim” because they are very colorful.</p><p>It is great, undoubtedly, to combine different collections from Amy Tangerine, because the colors combine fantastically.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1b952f3f167114a6.jpg?v=1782539880\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Moreover, I have used the words “Thank you” from the Thickers as a title for my project, accompanied with a chipboard from the collection “On a Whim”.</p><p>I have enjoyed so much to combine both of these elements because the result is quite funny in this Layout.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/399df38b98422f5e.jpg?v=1782539883\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>As a decorative element, I have used some mini enamel dots of different colors in different areas of the project, placing them randomly.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/be52128fbf37d097.jpg?v=1782539885\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Lastly, on the left side of the project, I cut a small piece of paper and placed a piece of a flowered patterned paper, to create more contrast in this project.</p><p>I hope that this project will be useful for you as a source of inspiration for your Scrap projects; and I also hope that you make the most of your transparent stickers from the different Amy Tangerine’s collections.</p><p>Violeta Scrap</p><p><a href=\"http://violetascrap.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/violeta_scrap/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/violeta_scrap\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VioletaScrap/\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/VioletaScrap\">YouTube</a></p><p>Supplies: Hustle &amp; Heart- 12x12 Double Sided Paper – Cut it out (341879), Hustle &amp; Heart- 12x12 Double Sided Paper – Floral sensation (341871), Oh happy life Collection - Thickers - Wild (376223), On a whim - Thickers - LOL (378746), On a whim Collection - Clear Stickers, On a whim Collection - Sticker Book (378748)</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing, Violeta! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now! Check your local retailer and online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/AThustleandheart\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vJOlKd\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
